text: Laraesima ochreoapicalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1973. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Laraesima ochreoapicalis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1973
